OL,5, BBC Question Time host Fiona Bruce says
OL,6, she will step back from her role as an 
OL,7, ambassador for the domestic violence   
OL,8, charity Refuge, following a comment she
OL,9, made on air about Stanley Johnson.     
OL,11,FBruce has been accused of trivialising 
OL,12,Fdomestic violence during a discussion  
OL,13,Fabout Johnson on last week's show.     
OL,15,FIn a statement, Bruce confirmed that   
OL,16,Fshe will be leaving her role "with real
OL,17,Fsadness".                              
OL,19,FShe added that her words has been      
OL,20,F"mischaracterised" in a "media storm". 
